EnumBusinessLocationClassification.description:
Classifies if the party is external or interal or other type of classifier for a party.  BL_CORPORATE	External business entity to Marsh.
BL_INDIVIDUAL	External individual entity to Marsh.
BL_INTERNAL	Clients that have been set up for accounting only purposes; typically not real business entities.
BL_CLASS_HIST	A once valid client entity that has had claims filed against it under one or more policies under which it was covered. The client could have gone out of business or been bought and sold by other companies since it was active in an invoicing system.
BL_SPECIAL	Special Projects that are set up with a real project name, but a pseudonymous address because the address is meaningless. These are typically not real business entities.
BL_CONFIDENTIAL	Prospect/Clients that are set up with pseudonymous names and addresses so as to completely conceal their identity.
